{"tid":816221,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一生只求有個女人每晚俾我攬住大脾訓","createTime":"2018-09-12T15:02:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T15:44:59.000Z","uid":58316,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ceee4cb3532820fe1044c4371e8fb08f5d008ce6","tid":816221,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T15:02:45.000Z","msg":"已經好俾心機考aco<br />\n而家揾萬頭<br />\n但我會上進<br />\n未必有樓<br />\n未必有車<br />\n但都叫afford得起<br />\n每月食一餐cheesecake factory<br />\n點解冇女人肯要我<br />\n返親工條條女都嫌棄我<br />\n如果我做到aco<br />\n你地會唔會對我改觀<br />\n會唔會食我整既散水餅<br />\n會唔會同我keep contact<br />\n會唔會倒追返我<br />\n同我分享三萬蚊頂薪<br />\n三萬<br />\n對你地黎講<br />\n係微不足道<br />\n阿頭揾七八萬<br />\n但佢有老婆<br />\n我冇女朋友<br />\n可以好放心<br />\n三萬蚊<br />\n除左自己搭車食飯<br />\n可以畀哂gf<br />\n為既<br />\n只係每晚有個女人俾我攬住大脾訓<br />\n做男人<br />\n放左工<br />\n返到去食完飯<br />\n有電視睇<br />\n有老婆扑<br />\n有女人大脾攬<br />\n仲想求咩"},{"pid":"28f0062e123e3e692076ca44e31ba397506eeb53","tid":816221,"uid":171310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T15:03:57.000Z","msg":"自己搵AUNTIE"},{"pid":"ab877cd03d8a30de043483ab98b69691c613dd61","tid":816221,"uid":208726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T15:10:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1513332fc4561eb2482c42c50ae62bca5a30ba27","tid":816221,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T15:11:16.000Z","msg":"充滿後現代控訴 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n樓主每日都"},{"pid":"9eae37cf6c9cc022f334307679da2c123e9bcaec","tid":816221,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1513332fc4561eb2482c42c50ae62bca5a30ba27","tid":816221,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T15:11:16.000Z","msg":"充滿後現代控訴 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n樓主每日都"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T15:44:59.000Z","msg":"有無前現袋"}]}